project: Pick up the creative bug in order to regain your creativity. Hitting (Key: O) the corresponding emotion block opens doors.
While angry, you can break through gates
Health Bugs heal you to full health
You are not able to cross gaps
While sad, you periodically gain a shield of tears.
And when cooking(Key: P) you throw a curved hotdog that can retrieve items.
